Package: heaven
Type: Package
Title: Data Preparation Routines for Medical Registry Data
Version: 2019.05.12
Author: Helene Charlotte Rytgaard, Anders Munch, Christian Torp-Pedersen, Jannik Pallisgaard, Regitze Kuhr Skals, Peter Enemark Lund, Thomas Alexander Gerds
